<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>The Hole in the Wall Café — Bangalore's Favorite Breakfast Spot</title>
  <meta name="description" content="The Hole in the Wall Café serves Bangalore's most beloved breakfasts. Fresh ingredients, warm ambiance, and soul-warming food in the heart of the city." />
  <meta name="keywords" content="breakfast café Bangalore, best breakfast Bangalore, brunch Bangalore, The Hole in the Wall Café" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="The Hole in the Wall Café" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Bangalore's Favorite Breakfast Spot. Book your table today." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,800;1,400;1,600&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&family=Dancing+Script:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --cream: #faf6f0;
      --cream-dark: #f2ebe0;
      --warm-white: #fffdf9;
      --brown-deep: #3b2314;
      --brown-mid: #6b3f26;
      --brown-light: #a0613a;
      --caramel: #c8885a;
      --caramel-light: #e2b48a;
      --gold: #d4a84b;
      --sage: #8a9e7f;
      --sage-light: #b8c9b0;
      --peach: #f4c9a8;
      --text-dark: #2c1a0e;
      --text-mid: #5c3d28;
      --text-light: #8a6850;
      --shadow-warm: rgba(107,63,38,0.15);
      --shadow-deep: rgba(59,35,20,0.25);
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 16px; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--text-dark);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── SCROLLBAR ── */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--cream-dark); }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--caramel); border-radius: 3px; }

    /* ── NAVBAR ── */
    #navbar {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      height: 72px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      transition: background 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease, height 0.3s ease;
    }
    #navbar.scrolled {
      background: rgba(250,246,240,0.97);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 20px var(--shadow-warm);
      height: 62px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; line-height: 1;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-logo span:first-child {
      font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--brown-deep);
    }
    .nav-logo span:last-child {
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--caramel);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--brown-deep);
      position: relative;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .nav-links a::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; bottom: -4px; left: 0; right: 100%;
      height: 1.5px; background: var(--caramel);
      transition: right 0.3s ease;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--caramel); }
    .nav-links a:hover::after { right: 0; }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--brown-deep);
      color: var(--cream) !important;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: background 0.3s !important;
    }
    .nav-cta::after { display: none !important; }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--caramel) !important; color: white !important; }

    /* hamburger */
    .hamburger {
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column; gap: 5px;
      cursor: pointer; padding: 4px;
      background: none; border: none;
    }
    .hamburger span {
      display: block; width: 24px; height: 2px;
      background: var(--brown-deep);
      transition: transform 0.3s, opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .hamburger.open span:nth-child(1) { transform: translateY(7px) rotate(45deg); }
    .hamburger.open span:nth-child(2) { opacity: 0; }
    .hamburger.open span:nth-child(3) { transform: translateY(-7px) rotate(-45deg); }

    .mobile-menu {
      display: none;
      position: fixed; top: 62px; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 999;
      background: rgba(250,246,240,0.98);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--shadow-deep);
      transform: translateY(-10px); opacity: 0;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
    }
    .mobile-menu.open { display: block; transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
    .mobile-menu ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
    .mobile-menu a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--brown-deep);
    }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    #hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      position: relative;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555396273-367ea4eb4db5?w=1600&q=80');
      background-size: cover; background-position: center;
      transform: scale(1.05);
      transition: transform 8s ease;
    }
    .hero-bg.loaded { transform: scale(1); }
    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        rgba(59,35,20,0.72) 0%,
        rgba(107,63,38,0.55) 40%,
        rgba(200,136,90,0.25) 100%
      );
    }
    .hero-content {
      position: relative; z-index: 2;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 820px;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--caramel-light);
      border: 1px solid rgba(226,180,138,0.5);
      padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
      animation: heroFadeUp 0.8s 0.3s forwards;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--warm-white);
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(25px);
      animation: heroFadeUp 0.9s 0.5s forwards;
    }
    .hero-title em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--caramel-light);
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.85);
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
      animation: heroFadeUp 0.9s 0.7s forwards;
    }
    .hero-btns {
      display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
      animation: heroFadeUp 0.9s 0.9s forwards;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--caramel);
      color: white;
      padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.82rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none; cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.3s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(200,136,90,0.4);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--gold);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(200,136,90,0.5);
    }
    .btn-outline {
      display: inline-block;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--warm-white);
      padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.82rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,253,249,0.7);
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover {
      background: rgba(255,253,249,0.15);
      border-color: var(--caramel-light);
      color: var(--caramel-light);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .hero-scroll {
      position: absolute; bottom: 2rem; left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.6);
      font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
      animation: bounce 2s infinite 2s;
    }
    .hero-scroll-line {
      width: 1px; height: 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,253,249,0.6), transparent);
    }
    @keyframes heroFadeUp {
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes bounce {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(6px); }
    }

    /* ── SECTIONS COMMON ── */
    section { padding: 6rem 2rem; }
    .section-label {
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--caramel);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--brown-deep);
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--caramel); }
    .section-divider {
      width: 48px; height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--caramel), var(--gold));
      margin: 1.25rem 0;
    }
    .section-divider.centered { margin: 1.25rem auto; }

    /* fade-in scroll animations */
    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(32px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
    }
    .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .fade-in-left {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-40px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
    }
    .fade-in-left.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
    .fade-in-right {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateX(40px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
    }
    .fade-in-right.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }

    /* ── ABOUT ── */
    #about { background: var(--warm-white); }
    .about-inner {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 5rem; align-items: center;
    }
    .about-img-wrap {
      position: relative;
    }
    .about-img-main {
      width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/5;
      object-fit: cover; border-radius: 4px;
      box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--caramel-light);
    }
    .about-img-accent {
      position: absolute;
      width: 48%; aspect-ratio: 1;
      object-fit: cover; border-radius: 4px;
      bottom: -2rem; right: -2rem;
      border: 5px solid var(--warm-white);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px var(--shadow-deep);
    }
    .about-badge {
      position: absolute; top: -1.5rem; left: -1.5rem;
      width: 80px; height: 80px;
      background: var(--brown-deep);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: var(--cream);
    }
    .about-badge strong {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1;
    }
    .about-badge span {
      font-size: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .about-text p {
      font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.85;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .about-stats {
      display: flex; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .stat { text-align: center; }
    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--caramel);
      display: block;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-light);
    }

    /* ── MENU ── */
    #menu { background: var(--cream); }
    .menu-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .menu-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .menu-tabs {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .menu-tab {
      padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      background: none; border: 1.5px solid var(--caramel-light);
      color: var(--text-mid); border-radius: 2px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.25s, color 0.25s, border-color 0.25s;
    }
    .menu-tab.active, .menu-tab:hover {
      background: var(--brown-deep);
      border-color: var(--brown-deep);
      color: var(--cream);
    }
    .menu-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .menu-card {
      background: var(--warm-white);
      border-radius: 4px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px var(--shadow-warm);
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
      display: none;
    }
    .menu-card.active { display: block; }
    .menu-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px var(--shadow-deep);
    }
    .menu-card-img {
      width: 100%; height: 180px;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    }
    .menu-card:hover .menu-card-img { transform: scale(1.06); }
    .menu-card-body { padding: 1.25rem; }
    .menu-card-name {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--brown-deep);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }
    .menu-card-desc {
      font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .menu-card-footer {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    }
    .menu-price {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--caramel);
    }
    .menu-tag {
      font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .tag-veg { background: #e8f5e9; color: #388e3c; }
    .tag-chef { background: var(--cream-dark); color: var(--caramel); }

    /* ── GALLERY ── */
    #gallery { background: var(--cream-dark); }
    .gallery-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .gallery-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      grid-template-rows: auto;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    .gallery-item {
      overflow: hidden; border-radius: 3px;
      position: relative; cursor: pointer;
    }
    .gallery-item:nth-child(1) { grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 2; }
    .gallery-item:nth-child(5) { grid-column: span 2; }
    .gallery-item img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover; display: block;
      transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    }
    .gallery-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.08); }
    .gallery-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: rgba(59,35,20,0);
      transition: background 0.3s;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .gallery-item:hover .gallery-overlay { background: rgba(59,35,20,0.25); }
    .gallery-icon {
      color: white; font-size: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.8);
      transition: opacity 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }
    .gallery-item:hover .gallery-icon { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }

    /* ── RESERVATION ── */
    #reservation { background: var(--brown-deep); }
    .reservation-inner {
      max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
      gap: 5rem; align-items: start;
    }
    .reservation-info .section-label { color: var(--caramel-light); }
    .reservation-info .section-title { color: var(--warm-white); }
    .reservation-info .section-divider { background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--caramel), var(--gold)); }
    .reservation-info p {
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.7);
      font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.85;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .res-contact {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.85rem;
    }
    .res-contact-item {
      display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .res-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      background: rgba(255,253,249,0.08);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    .res-contact-item span {
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.75);
      font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .res-form {
      background: rgba(255,253,249,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,253,249,0.1);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.6);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .form-group input, .form-group select {
      width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      background: rgba(255,253,249,0.07);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,253,249,0.12);
      border-radius: 3px;
      color: var(--warm-white);
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
      outline: none;
    }
    .form-group input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,253,249,0.3); }
    .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus {
      border-color: var(--caramel);
      background: rgba(255,253,249,0.1);
    }
    .form-group select option { background: var(--brown-mid); }
    .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
    .btn-submit {
      width: 100%; padding: 0.9rem;
      background: var(--caramel);
      color: white;
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.82rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
      border: none; border-radius: 3px; cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }
    .btn-submit:hover { background: var(--gold); transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .form-success {
      display: none;
      text-align: center; padding: 2rem;
      color: var(--caramel-light);
    }
    .form-success .checkmark { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .form-success h3 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--warm-white);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .form-success p { color: rgba(255,253,249,0.6); font-size: 0.9rem; }

    /* ── REVIEWS ── */
    #reviews { background: var(--warm-white); }
    .reviews-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .reviews-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
    .reviews-slider {
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .reviews-track {
      display: flex; gap: 1.5rem;
      transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
    .review-card {
      min-width: calc(33.333% - 1rem);
      background: var(--cream);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px var(--shadow-warm);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .review-stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .review-text {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .reviewer { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: center; }
    .reviewer-img {
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;
      border: 2px solid var(--caramel-light);
    }
    .reviewer-info strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brown-deep);
    }
    .reviewer-info span {
      font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-light);
    }
    .slider-controls {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }
    .slider-btn {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--caramel-light);
      background: none; cursor: pointer;
      color: var(--caramel);
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .slider-btn:hover { background: var(--brown-deep); color: white; border-color: var(--brown-deep); }
    .slider-dots { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; }
    .dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%; background: var(--caramel-light);
      cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }
    .dot.active { background: var(--caramel); transform: scale(1.4); }

    /* ── LOCATION ── */
    #location { background: var(--cream); }
    .location-inner {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr;
      gap: 4rem; align-items: start;
    }
    .location-info .section-divider { margin: 1rem 0; }
    .location-detail {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem;
    }
    .loc-item {
      display: flex; gap: 0.85rem; align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .loc-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      background: var(--cream-dark);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      color: var(--caramel); font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .loc-item strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-light);
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }
    .loc-item p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.65; }
    .map-wrap {
      border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--shadow-deep);
      height: 420px;
    }
    .map-wrap iframe { width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; display: block; }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: var(--brown-deep);
      padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem;
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.7);
    }
    .footer-inner {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,253,249,0.1);
    }
    .footer-brand .nav-logo span:first-child { color: var(--cream); font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .footer-brand .nav-logo span:last-child { color: var(--caramel-light); }
    .footer-brand p {
      margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.75;
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.55);
    }
    .footer-social {
      display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .social-btn {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,253,249,0.2);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.7);
      text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    }
    .social-btn:hover {
      background: var(--caramel);
      border-color: var(--caramel);
      color: white;
    }
    .footer-col h4 {
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.9);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .footer-links { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
    .footer-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.55);
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--caramel-light); }
    .hours-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .hours-item {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,253,249,0.55);
    }
    .hours-item span:last-child { color: rgba(255,253,249,0.8); }
    .footer-bottom {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 2rem auto 0;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,253,249,0.35);
    }

    /* ── LIGHTBOX ── */
    .lightbox {
      display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 2000;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.92);
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .lightbox.open { display: flex; }
    .lightbox img { max-width: 90vw; max-height: 85vh; border-radius: 3px; }
    .lightbox-close {
      position: absolute; top: 1.5rem; right: 1.5rem;
      color: white; font-size: 2rem; cursor: pointer;
      background: none; border: none; line-height: 1;
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .gallery-item:nth-child(1) { grid-column: span 2; }
      .gallery-item:nth-child(5) { grid-column: span 1; }
      .review-card { min-width: calc(50% - 0.75rem); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hamburger { display: flex; }
      section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
      .about-inner,
      .reservation-inner,
      .location-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .about-img-accent { display: none; }
      .about-badge { top: 1rem; left: 1rem; }
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .gallery-item:nth-child(1) { grid-column: span 2; aspect-ratio: 16/9; }
      .gallery-item:nth-child(5) { grid-column: span 2; }
      .review-card { min-width: 85vw; }
      .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .about-stats { gap: 1.25rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAVBAR -->
<nav id="navbar" role="navigation" aria-label="Main navigation">
  <a href="#hero" class="nav-logo" aria-label="The Hole in the Wall Café Home">
    <span>The Hole in the Wall</span>
    <span>Café &amp; Breakfast Bar · Bangalore</span>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links" role="list">
    <li><a href="#about">Our Story</a></li>
    <li><a href="#menu">Menu</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gallery">Gallery</a></li>
    <li><a href="#reviews">Reviews</a></li>
    <li><a href="#location">Visit Us</a></li>
    <li><a href="#reservation" class="nav-cta">Book a Table</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Toggle menu" aria-expanded="false">
    <span></span><span></span><span></span>
  </button>
</nav>

<div class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu" role="navigation" aria-label="Mobile navigation">
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#about" class="mobile-link">Our Story</a></li>
    <li><a href="#menu" class="mobile-link">Menu</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gallery" class="mobile-link">Gallery</a></li>
    <li><a href="#reviews" class="mobile-link">Reviews</a></li>
    <li><a href="#location" class="mobile-link">Visit Us</a></li>
    <li><a href="#reservation" class="mobile-link">Book a Table</a></li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero" aria-label="Hero">
  <div class="hero-bg" id="heroBg"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">Est. 2011 · Indiranagar, Bangalore</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Bangalore's <em>Favourite</em><br>Breakfast Spot</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Where mornings taste like they were made just for you. Slow-cooked plates, single-origin pour-overs, and a corner table with your name on it.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#menu" class="btn-primary">Explore Our Menu</a>
      <a href="#reservation" class="btn-outline">Reserve a Table</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="hero-scroll-line"></div>
    <span>Scroll</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div class="about-img-wrap fade-in-left">
      <div class="about-badge"><strong>13</strong><span>Years</span></div>
      <img class="about-img-main" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600093463592-8e36ae95ef56?w=800&q=80" alt="Inside The Hole in the Wall Café" loading="lazy" />
      <img class="about-img-accent" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1495474472287-4d71bcdd2085?w=400&q=80" alt="Coffee at the café" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="about-text fade-in-right">
      <p class="section-label">Our Story</p>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="about-title">A Little Café<br>With a Big <em>Heart</em></h2>
      <div class="section-divider"></div>
      <p>It started with a stubborn belief — that breakfast deserves the same care as any fine-dining experience. In 2011, we opened a tiny, seventeen-seater café in a lane off Indiranagar, and the neighbourhood adopted us overnight.</p>
      <p>We source our eggs from a family farm in Chickballapur, our coffee from a single-origin estate in Coorg, and our bread is baked in-house every morning from 5 a.m. None of that has changed in thirteen years.</p>
      <p>What started as a hole in the wall has grown into a community — a place where regulars know each other by name and first-timers always come back.</p>
      <div class="about-stats">
        <div class="stat fade-in" style="transition-delay:0.1s">
          <span class="stat-num">13+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Years Open</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat fade-in" style="transition-delay:0.2s">
          <span class="stat-num">180+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Seats</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat fade-in" style="transition-delay:0.3s">
          <span class="stat-num">4.8★</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Google Rating</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat fade-in" style="transition-delay:0.4s">
          <span class="stat-num">42k</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Happy Guests</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MENU -->
<section id="menu" aria-labelledby="menu-title">
  <div class="menu-inner">
    <div class="menu-header fade-in">
      <p class="section-label">What We Serve</p>
