        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="review-text">"Honestly the best breakfast I have had in Bangalore. The Eggs Benedict is a religious experience. I've been coming every weekend for two years and the quality never dips."</p>
          <div class="reviewer">
            <img class="reviewer-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=100&q=80" alt="Ananya Krishnamurthy" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="reviewer-info">
