              <span>Indiranagar regular · Google Review</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="review-text">"The filter coffee alone is worth the trip. You can taste the difference between this and any chain café. Cozy, unhurried, and the staff remember your name. That's rare."</p>
          <div class="reviewer">
            <img class="reviewer-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=100&q=80" alt="Rohit Menon" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="reviewer-info">
              <strong>Rohit Menon</strong>
              <span>Koramangala · Zomato Review</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="review-text">"Brought my parents here on their visit to Bangalore. They kept asking me why we don't have something like this in Chennai. The Brunch Board for two is an absolute spread."</p>
          <div class="reviewer">
            <img class="reviewer-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?w=100&q=80" alt="Deepika Subramaniam" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="reviewer-info">
              <strong>Deepika Subramaniam</strong>
              <span>Whitefield · Instagram</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="review-text">"I work remotely and this is my office two mornings a week. The Wi-Fi is fast, the music is just right, and the Matcha Latte is the only reason I get out of bed before 9."</p>
          <div class="reviewer">
            <img class="reviewer-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?w=100&q=80" alt="Kiran Rao" loading="lazy" />
