              <span>HSR Layout · Google Review</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="review-text">"Came for a birthday brunch and they set up the table so beautifully without me asking. The pancakes had a candle on them. Little things like that make a place worth returning to."</p>
          <div class="reviewer">
            <img class="reviewer-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?w=100&q=80" alt="Meera Pillai" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="reviewer-info">
              <strong>Meera Pillai</strong>
              <span>Jayanagar · Swiggy Dineout</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
